DEFINE MOTIF Transformations

 P C4  B3  G   A  G  F  G  C4   D  E  F  D   C
 R 2   4   4   4  8  8  4  4    8  8  8  8   2
END Transformations

TEMPO 2 = 120
NOTELIST USING 2-4
PERFORM Transformations         /* Straight performance */
P . 
R 1
PERFORM Transformations (T(G))  /* Tonal transposition */
P .
R 1
PERFORM Transformations (ST(G)) /* Strict transposition */
P .
R 1
PERFORM Transformations (I)     /* Tonal inversion */
P .
R 1
PERFORM Transformations (SI)    /* Strict inversion */
P .
R 1
PERFORM Transformations (R)     /* Retrograde performance */
P . 
R 1
PERFORM Transformations (PR)    /* Pitch-only retrograde */
P .
R 1
PERFORM Transformations (RR)    /* Rhythm-only retrograde */
END
